Description: a dependency-free, header-only library of templates providing well-defined
semantics for safely and performantly handling a variety of numeric operations.

Branch and folder URL is https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/src/+/refs/heads/master/base/numerics/

Local Modifications: Updated using do-updates.sh, which performs trivial renames (namespace, header
guards, etc.) and generates an appropriate BUILD.gn file.

Upstream changes should be preferred and mirrored here.
